Uttar Pradesh
Sep 25, 2014
Child Sexual Abuse, Molestation
Description:
			Three youths made an attempt to rape a 16-year-old girl when she was on her way to the fields in Shamli district, police said.

Sohanvir, Monu and Ravi had abducted the victim when she was carrying lunch to her father in Abdannagar village under Jhinjhana police station yesterday, police said.

The victim was taken to a sugarcane field where she started crying and shouting and opposed the rape attempt, attracting attention of passersby, they added.

The youths then dumped her and escaped from the scene of crime, police said, adding, a case against the three in this connection.


